Package: pbwg.eurocontrol
Type: Package
Title: PBWG Wrappers for EUROCONTROL Data
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Quinten GOENS", "EUROCONTROL PRU", email = "quinten.goens@eurocontrol.int", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides R-native wrappers around the EUROCONTROL data access
    helpers to provide inputs for PBWG reports. The package
    exposes high-level functions for NM area traffic, market segments, DAIO
    breakdowns, APDF airport operator dataflows, and compound CHN-EUR traffic
    summaries, all powered by the eurocontrol package and ROracle.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: false
